oteomic analyses reported in Figures 6 and Supplementary File 1 can be found at https://www.thewakefieldlab.com/ms; the significantly reduced protein IDs for each RNAi experiment  were interrogated using a Gene Ontology (GO) classifier (GOTermMapper (https://go.princeton.edu/cgi-bin/GOTermMapper), concentrating on the GO terms &quot;&quot;cell division&quot;&quot; (GO:0051301), &quot;&quot;mitotic cell cycle&quot;&quot; (GO:0000278) and &quot;&quot;chromosome segregation&quot;&quot; (GO:0007059). Source data files have been provided for Figures 1, 4, 5, 7, 8, and 9.</p></sec><supplementary-material><ext-link xlink:href="elife-40325-supp-v1.zip">Download zip</ext-link><p>Any figures and tables for this article are included in the PDF. The zip folder contains additional supplemental files.</p></supplementary-material></sec></back></article>